{"tid":640604,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"識唱一齊唱 衝力射波","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:14:07.000Z","uid":182001,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"239946bf80fbf3dc93dce9a3cfa82b07904fa8e4","tid":640604,"uid":182001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚睇左個靚廣告，今日忍唔住就改左呢首歌<br />\n<br />\n識唱一齊唱  <br />\n衝力射波  原曲：足球小將 張衛健<br />\n改詞：大B #二次音樂<br />\n<br />\n看看威風的他<br />\n天天追趕Order<br />\n七點放工頂呱呱<br />\n我波士都稱讚他<br />\n<br />\n收工啦！好嗎 (收工啦！好嗎)<br />\nOT 最耍家 (OT 他最耍家)<br />\n最愛拼搏 日做夜做<br />\n真陰功 無花假<br />\n<br />\n放得早 跨啦啦<br />\n落力拼勁 加兩吧<br />\n射波招式創新<br />\nSick Leave不會假<br />\n<br />\n工呀工 無返工<br />\n射呀射 射波吧<br />\n攞得好 放三天假 (放鬆一吓)<br />\nOT嗎 只有他"},{"pid":"f90954fad6d935ffd5e67fc88afbe6cdb803c063","tid":640604,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名等聽"},{"pid":"51c4309627778cbe7afe4dad29f4dbd2d94fdcc8","tid":640604,"uid":58690,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"好撚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172c12f7f865cfc113c117c4445c50dc3d3c6223","tid":640604,"uid":110876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51c4309627778cbe7afe4dad29f4dbd2d94fdcc8","tid":640604,"uid":58690,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"好撚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾好喎有乜咁尷尬"},{"pid":"00c5c0dcb49599a710d04efe05c7629c9d73467e","tid":640604,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84942609ed78baea6290d240c7dd7339d0bab09